256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 20-year-old Sarno saw her Olympic debut come to a quick halt as she failed to make a lift in the snatch portion of the women's 71kg division at the South Paris Arena on Friday, August 9 (Saturday, August 10, Manila time).\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 420, \"end\": 425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarno\", \"score\": 0.9986709118989777, \"rank\": 0.0013308504666215651, \"text\": \"Sarno\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarno\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarno\"}, {\"begin\": 556, \"end\": 567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Paris,_Maine\", \"score\": 0.9999999957976797, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"South Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Paris,_Maine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Paris,_Maine\"}, {\"begin\": 616, \"end\": 622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\", \"score\": 0.9885536582706653, \"rank\": 0.006374691462570243, \"text\": \"Manila\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She registered a DNF (did not finish) after using up all her three snatch attempts at 100kg to no success.\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 737, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olivia Reeves lived up to her billing as the heavy favorite, winning the United States' first Olympic weightlifting gold since the 2000 Sydney Games as she topped the field with a 262kg total.\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 931, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 739, \"end\": 745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Pope\", \"score\": 0.8341618560603696, \"rank\": 0.19880510605963084, \"text\": \"Olivia\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.