xpected early exit for Sarno, considering she placed fourth in the Olympic Qualification Ranking of the International Weightlifting Federation (IWF).\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1104, \"end\": 1109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarno\", \"score\": 0.9986709118989777, \"rank\": 0.0013308504666215651, \"text\": \"Sarno\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarno\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarno\"}, {\"begin\": 1185, \"end\": 1223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Weightlifting_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Weightlifting Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Weightlifting_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Weightlifting_Federation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also, Sarno has shown she is capable of clearing heavier weights in snatch as she lifted a national record of 110kg in theIWF World Cupin Phuket, Thailand, in April.\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1397, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1238, \"end\": 1243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarno\", \"score\": 0.9986709118989777, \"rank\": 0.0013308504666215651, \"text\": \"Sarno\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarno\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarno\"}, {\"begin\": 1364, \"end\": 1369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cupin_superfamily\", \"score\": 0.9999999175813662, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cupin\", \"types\": [\"Q8054\", \"Q206229\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cupin_superfamily\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cupin_superfamily\"}, {\"begin\": 1370, \"end\": 1376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phuket_province\", \"score\": 0.9999110206564209, \"rank\": 8.898712370968019e-05, \"text\": \"Phuket\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phuket_province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phuket_province\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even in theSoutheast Asian Games, where she is a two-time gold medalist, the pride of Tagbilaran, Bohol, owns the meet record in snatch with 105kg.\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1546, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1485, \"end\": 1495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tagbilaran\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.2694230199200645e-12, \"text\": \"Tagbilaran\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tagbilaran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tagbilaran\"}, {\"begin\": 1497, \"end\": 1502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bohol\", \"score\": 0.9895453166783644, \"rank\": 0.01056513838843203, \"text\": \"Bohol\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bohol\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bohol\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sarno suffered the same fate as teammateJohn Ceniza, who also tallied a DNF in the men's 61kg category after being unable to make a successful lift in the snatch round.\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1716, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"OnlyElreen Andoout of the three Filipino weightlifters who qualified for the Olympics went all the way as she finished sixth in the women's 59kg class.- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1912, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1750, \"end\": 1758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9996951100749969, \"rank\": 0.00029844294041436677, \"text\": \"Filipino\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}, {\"begin\": 1871, \"end\": 1882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rappler.com\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\", \"dbpedia\": \"h